ewsnetwork.com/news/2016-06-05/former-spja-ceo-marc-perez-joins-anime-matsuri/.102862|accessdate=14 June 2016|work=Anime News Network|date=June 5, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cb02222018\">{{cite news |last1=Ayres |first1=Andrea |title=How #MeToo Helped Revitalize The Boycott Anime Matsuri Movement |url=https://www.comicsbeat.com/how-metoo-helped-revitalize-the-boycott-anime-matsuri-movement/ |accessdate=16 June 2019 |work=The Beat |date=22 February 2018}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cw04072017\">{{cite news|last1=Rouege|first1=Ciara|title=PHOTOS: Cosplayers invade Houston in jaw-dropping fits for Anime Matsuri|url=http://cw39.com/2017/04/07/photos-cosplayers-invade-houston-in-jaw-dropping-fits-for-anime-matsuri/|accessdate=29 May 2017|work=Newsfix CW39|date=April 7, 2017}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=fph03182014>{{cite news|last=Haydon|first=DL|title=Anime Matsuri: The Good, the Bad and the Ugly|url=http://www.freepresshouston.com/anime-matsuri-the-good-the-bad-and-the-ugly/|accessdate=18 April 2014|newspaper=Free Press Houston|date=March 18, 2014}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"hc04042015\">{{cite news|last1=Hlavaty|first1=Craig|title=The cosplay-heavy Anime Matsuri invades the George R. Brown Convention|url=http://www.chron.com/entertainment/article/The-cosplay-heavy-Anime-Matsuri-invades-the-6179241.php|accessdate=16 April 2015|work=Houston Chronicle|date=April 4, 2015}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"hc03282018\">{{cite news |last1=Darling |first1=Cary |title=Houston\u2019s Anime Matsuri festival draws sexual-harassment controversy |url=https://www.chron.com/life/article/Houston-s-Anime-Matsuri-festival-draws-12789687.php |accessdate=16 June 2019 |work=Houston Chronicle |date=28 March 2018}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=houstonia03312015>{{cite news|last1=Berardo|first1=Maggie|title=Turning Japanese, Houston-Style|url=http://www.houstoniamag.com/arts-and-entertainment/on-the-town/articles/april-is-east-asian-month-in-houston-march-2015|accessdate=16 April 2015|work=Houstonia|date=March 31, 2015}}</ref>\n\n