{"title_page": "Szewska Street, Krak\u00f3w", "text_new": "{{Infobox street\n| name                    = Szewska Street\n| marker_image            = \n| native_name             = \n| native_name_lang        = \n| alternate_name          =\n| image                   = Szewska street, view to NW, Old Town, Krakow, Poland.jpg\n| image_size              = 300\n| image_alt               =\n| image_map               = Krakow Center - Ulica Szewska.svg\n| caption                 = View from junction with [[Jagiello\u0144ska Street, Krak\u00f3w|Jagiello\u0144ska Street]] towards the north-west. [[Bagatela Theatre]] on the horizon.\n| map_type                =\n| map_size                =\n| map_caption             =\n| map_alt                 =\n| other_name              =\n| former_names            =\n| part_of                 =\n| namesake                =\n| type                    =\n| owner                   =\n| maint                   =\n| length                  =\n| length_m                = 270\n| length_ft               =\n| length_km               =\n| length_mi               =\n| length_ref              =\n| length_notes            =\n| width                   =\n| area                    =\n| addresses               =\n| location                =\n| arrondissement          =\n| quarter                 =\n| postal_code             =\n| metro                   =\n| coordinates             =\n| direction_a             = West\n| terminus_a              = Podwale Street\n| direction_b             = East\n| terminus_b              = [[Krak\u00f3w Old Town|Main Square]]\n| junction                = \n| north                   =\n| east                    =\n| south                   =\n| west                    =\n| main_contractor         =\n| cost                    =\n| references              =\n| commissioning_date      =\n| construction_start_date =\n| completion_date         =\n| inauguration_date       = \n| demolition_date         =\n| designer                =\n| known_for               =\n| status                  =\n| website                 = \n}}\n\n'''Szewska Street''' ([[Polish language|Polish]]: ''Ulica Szewska'', lit. Shoemakers Street) - a historic street in [[Krak\u00f3w]], Poland. The street begins at the [[Krak\u00f3w Old Town|Main Square]] from which it heads west, where it adjoins Podwale Street. Formerly, where Szewska met with Podwale Street stood the former suburb of Garbary with [[Gristmill|gristmills]] and royal [[Fulling|fulling houses]]. Most of the street's buildings were built between the fourteenth and seventeenth-century. Szewska Street was part of the former [[Silesia|Silesian]] Route (heading towards [[Bytom]]). The street continues west as Karmelicka Street (''Ulica Karmelicka'', lit. Carmelites Street).<ref>{{cite web|title=Ulica Szewska w Krakowie {{!}} Ulice miasta Krakowa|url=http://www.krakow4u.pl/Ulica_Szewska_w_Krakowie.html|website=www.krakow4u.pl|accessdate=17 April 2017}}</ref>  \n\n==Features==\n{|\n|----- bgcolor=\"#FF 8C 00\"\n! width=4%  | Street No.\n! width=26% | Short description\n! width=10%  | Picture\n|----- bgcolor=\"#FFF8E1\"\n| align=\"center\"| 24 || align=\"center\"| '''Kantorowska House''' - a [[Classicism|Classicist]] building, which between 1977 and 2014 housed the traditional ''U Zalipianek'' restaurant. The building's interior is decorated with [[folk art]], designed by artists from the village of [[Zalipie, Lesser Poland Voivodeship|Zalipie]].<ref>{{cite web|last1=Maciejowski|first1=Arkadiusz|title=Krak\u00f3w. Zalipianki przegra\u0142y walk\u0119 o przetrwanie|url=http://www.gazetakrakowska.pl/artykul/3599977,krakow-zalipianki-przegraly-walke-o-przetrwanie,id,t.html|website=Gazetakrakowska.pl|accessdate=17 April 2017|language=pl}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=\u201eU Zalipianek\u201d po remoncie|url=https://telewizja.krakow.pl/?videos=kultowa-krakowska-kawiarnio-restauracja-u-zalipianek-wkrotce-powita-gosci|website=telewizja.krakow.pl|accessdate=17 April 2017|language=pl-PL|date=22 February 2017}}</ref> || align=\"center\"| [[Image:\u201eZalipianki Ewa Wachowicz\u201d resto bar, 24 Szewska street, Krak\u00f3w, Poland.jpg|100px]]\n|}\n\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Streets in Krak\u00f3w]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox street\n| name                    = Szewska Street\n| marker_image            = \n| native_name             = \n| native_name_lang        = \n| alternate_name          =\n| image                   = Szewska street, view to NW, Old Town, Krakow, Poland.jpg\n| image_size              = 300\n| image_alt               =\n| image_map               = Krakow Center - Ulica Szewska.svg\n| caption                 = View from junction with [[Jagiello\u0144ska Street, Krak\u00f3w|Jagiello\u0144ska Street]] towards the north-west. [[Bagatela Theatre]] on the horizon.\n| map_type                =\n| map_size                =\n| map_caption             =\n| map_alt                 =\n| other_name              =\n| former_names            =\n| part_of                 =\n| namesake                =\n| type                    =\n| owner                   =\n| maint                   =\n| length                  =\n| length_m                = 270\n| length_ft               =\n| length_km               =\n| length_mi               =\n| length_ref              =\n| length_notes            =\n| width                   =\n| area                    =\n| addresses               =\n| location                =\n| arrondissement          =\n| quarter                 =\n| postal_code             =\n| metro                   =\n| coordinates             =\n| direction_a             = West\n| terminus_a              = Podwale Street\n| direction_b             = East\n| terminus_b              = [[Krak\u00f3w Old Town|Main Square]]\n| junction                = \n| north                   =\n| east                    =\n| south                   =\n| west                    =\n| main_contractor         =\n| cost                