i wa ichido suteru mono''|\u547d\u306f\u4e00\u5ea6\u6368\u3066\u308b\u3082\u306e|extra=\"Life is for throwing away one time\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1976\n*{{nihongo|''Sanzu no kawa wa hitori de watare''|\u4e09\u9014\u306e\u5ddd\u306f\u72ec\u308a\u3067\u6e21\u308c|extra=\"Cross the [[Sanzu River]] Alone\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1977\n*{{nihongo|''Nido to ogamenu mikazuki''|\u4e8c\u5ea6\u3068\u62dd\u3081\u306c\u4e09\u65e5\u6708|extra=\"A Crescent Moon You Will Never Again Behold\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1977\n*{{nihongo|''\u014cshuji nanoka no shiss\u014d''|\u5965\u5dde\u8def\u30fb\u4e03\u65e5\u306e\u75be\u8d70|extra=\"Path to [[Mutsu Province|\u014cshu]], a Seven-day Speed-Race\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1978\n*{{nihongo|''Shin Kogarashi Monjir\u014d: Matte chitta t\u014dgebana''|\u65b0\u30fb\u6728\u67af\u3057\u7d0b\u6b21\u90ce \u821e\u3063\u3066\u6563\u3063\u305f\u5ce0\u82b1|extra=\"New Kogarashi Monjiro: the Mountain-Pass Flower that Danced and Scattered\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1988\n\n====Return of Kogarashi Monjiro series====\n*{{nihongo|''Kaette kita Kogarashi Monjir\u014d''|\u5e30\u3063\u3066\u6765\u305f\u6728\u67af\u3057\u7d0b\u6b21\u90ce|extra=\"The Return of Kogarashi Monjiro\"}}, [[Shinchosha]], 1996\n*{{nihongo|''Onajiku hitogoroshi''|\u540c\u3058\u304f\u4eba\u6bba\u3057|extra=\"Likewise a Killer\"}}<!--, Shinchosha-->, 1996\n*{{nihongo|''Kadowakashi''|\u304b\u3069\u308f\u304b\u3057|extra=\"Abduction\"}}<!--, Shinchosha-->, 1997\n*{{nihongo|''Saraba temari-uta''|\u3055\u3089\u3070\u624b\u97a0\u5504|extra=\"Farewell [[temari (toy)|Ball-bouncing]]-song\"}}<!--, Shinchosha-->, 1998\n*{{nihongo|''Akujo wo kiru toki''|\u60aa\u5973\u3092\u65ac\u308b\u3068\u304d|extra=\"When Sword-slaying an Evil Woman\"}}<!--, Shinchosha-->, 1999\n*{{nihongo|''Saig no t\u014dge-goe''|\u6700\u5f8c\u306e\u5ce0\u8d8a\u3048|extra=\"The Final Surmounting of the Mountain-pass\"}}<!--, Shinchosha-->, 1999\n\n====Downfall: Rise and Fall of the Tokugawa Cabinet====\n#{{nihongo|''Kan'ei no ishin tachi''