e [[K\u1e63itigarbha#K\u1e63itigarbha as Lord of the Six Ways|Six Jizo]]'s Shadows\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1972\n*{{nihongo|''Akatsuki no oiwake ni tatsu''|\u6681\u306e\u8ffd\u5206\u306b\u7acb\u3064|extra=\"Standing at the Fork in the Road at Dawn\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1972\n*{{nihongo|''Yonakiishi wa kiri ni nureta''|\u591c\u6ce3\u304d\u77f3\u306f\u9727\u306b\u6fe1\u308c\u305f|extra=\"The {{illm|Yonaki-ishi{{!}}Night-wailing stone|ja|\u591c\u6ce3\u304d\u77f3}} Dampened in the Fog\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1972\n*{{nihongo|''Onnen-zaka wo hotaru ga koeta''|\u6028\u5ff5\u5742\u3092\u87a2\u304c\u8d8a\u3048\u305f|extra=\"Fireflies over Grudge Hill\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1973\n*{{nihongo|''Fue ga nagareta Karisaka t\u014dge''|\u7b1b\u304c\u6d41\u308c\u305f\u96c1\u5742\u5ce0|extra=\"Flute sounded on {{illm|Karisaka Pass|ja|\u96c1\u5742\u5ce0}}\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1973\n*{{nihongo|''Kirisame ni nido naita''|\u9727\u96e8\u306b\u4e8c\u5ea6\u54ed\u3044\u305f|extra=\"Cried twice in the Misty Rain\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1976\n*{{nihongo|''Inochi wa ichido suteru mono''|\u547d\u306f\u4e00\u5ea6\u6368\u3066\u308b\u3082\u306e|extra=\"Life is for throwing away one time\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1976\n*{{nihongo|''Sanzu no kawa wa hitori de watare''|\u4e09\u9014\u306e\u5ddd\u306f\u72ec\u308a\u3067\u6e21\u308c|extra=\"Cross the [[Sanzu River]] Alone\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1977\n*{{nihongo|''Nido to ogamenu mikazuki''|\u4e8c\u5ea6\u3068\u62dd\u3081\u306c\u4e09\u65e5\u6708|extra=\"A Crescent Moon You Will Never Again Behold\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1977\n*{{nihongo|''\u014cshuji nanoka no shiss\u014d''|\u5965\u5dde\u8def\u30fb\u4e03\u65e5\u306e\u75be\u8d70|extra=\"Path to [[Mutsu Province|\u014cshu]], a Seven-day Speed-Race\"}}<!--, Kodansha-->, 1978\n*{{nihongo|''Shin Kogarashi Monjir\u014d: Matte chitta t\u014dgebana''|\u65b0\u30fb\u6728\u67af\u3057\u7d0b\u6b21\u90ce \u821e\u3063\u3066\u6563\u3063\u305f\u5ce0\u82b1|extra=\"New Kogarashi Monjiro: the Mountain-Pass Flower that Danced and Scattered\