uma Okitsugu]]'s Profound Schemes\"}}<!--, Shodensha-->, 1996-12\n#{{nihongo|''Kurofune to saigo no kenryokusha tachi''|\u9ed2\u8239\u3068\u6700\u5f8c\u306e\u6a29\u529b\u8005\u305f\u3061|extra=\"The Black Ships and the Last Power-wielders\"}}<!--, Shodensha-->, 1997-09\n* Shodensha Bunko format\n#{{nihongo|''J\u014dkan: Yab\u014d no geba sh\u014dgun''|\u4e0a\u5dfb \u91ce\u671b\u306e\u4e0b\u99ac\u5c06\u8ecd|extra=\"Volume One: The Ambitious [[Sakai Tadakiyo|Geba Shogun]]\"}}<!--, Shodensha Bunko-->, 2002-01\n#{{nihongo|''Ch\u016bkan: Sh\u014dgun Yoshimune no Inb\u014d''|\u4e2d\u5dfb \u5c06\u8ecd\u5409\u5b97\u306e\u9670\u8b00|extra=\"Volume Two: Shogun Yoshimune's Conspiracy\"}}<!--, Shodensha Bunko-->, 2002\u201303\n#{{nihongo|''Gekan: Kurofune j\u014dran''|\u4e0b\u5dfb \u9ed2\u8239\u64fe\u4e71|extra=\"Volume Three: The Black Ship Pandemonium\"}}<!--, Shodensha Bunko-->, 2002\u201305\n\n====[[Miyamoto Musashi]] series====\n#{{nihongo|''Musashi yaburetari''|\u6b66\u8535\u6557\u308c\u305f\u308a|extra=\"Musashi, You Are Defeated\"}}, [[Bungeishunj\u016b]], 1990-01\n#{{nihongo|''Ware jashin ariki''|\u308f\u308c\u90aa\u5fc3\u3042\u308a\u304d|extra=\"I Harbor Nefarious Thoughts\"}}<!--, [[Bungeishunj\u016b]]-->, 1990-02\n#{{nihongo|''Omei harasu ni oyobazu''|\u6c5a\u540d\u6674\u3089\u3059\u306b\u53ca\u3070\u305a|extra=\"No Need to Clear My Name\"}}<!--, [[Bungeishunj\u016b]]-->, 1990-03\n#{{nihongo|''Waga ik\u014d tattobu beshi''|\u308f\u304c\u5a01\u5149\u5c0a\u3076\u3079\u3057|extra=\"Venerate thee My Splendour\"}} <!--, [[Bungeishunj\u016b]]-->, 1990-08\n#{{nihongo|''Ware shisuru nari''|\u308f\u308c\u6b7b\u3059\u308b\u306a\u308a|extra=\"I shall Die\"}}<!--, [[Bungeishunj\u016b]]-->, 1991-02\n#{{nihongo|''En tachigatashi''|\u7e01\u65ad\u3061\u304c\u305f\u3057|extra=\"The Bond is Difficult to Sever\"}}<!--, [[Bungeishunj\u016b]]-->, 1991-08\n#{{nihongo|''Gishin osoruru beshi''|\u7591\u5fc3\u6050\u308b\u3079\u3057|extra=\"Suspicious-mindedness is to be Feared\"}}<!--, [[Bun