b.com/title/tt0285427/ Akuma no heya (1982)]\" on [[IMDb]]</ref>{{sfnp|Et\u014d|2005|p=148}}\n\n===TV Dramas===\n====TV series====\n*{{nihongo|''Kogarashi Monjir\u014d''|\u6728\u67af\u3057\u7d0b\u6b21\u90ce|extra=\"Kogarashi Monjiro\", 1972}}, Fuji TV.{{sfnp|Clements|Tamamuro|2003|p=198}}\n*{{nihongo|''Zoku Kogarashi Monjir\u014d''|\u7d9a\u30fb\u6728\u67af\u3057\u7d0b\u6b21\u90ce|extra=\"Kogarashi Monjiro, the Continuation\", 1972-73}}, Fuji TV.<ref name=nawata&nagata/>\n*{{nihongo|''Shin Kogarashi Monjir\u014d''|\u65b0\u30fb\u6728\u67af\u3057\u7d0b\u6b21\u90ce|extra=\"The New Kogarashi Monjiro\", 1977-78}}, [[Tokyo 12 Channel Television]].<ref>\"[https://www.imdb.com/title/tt8796242/ Shin Kogarashi Monjir\u00f4 (TV Series 1977\u20131978)]\" on [[IMDb]]</ref><ref name=nawata&nagata/>\n*{{nihongo|''Sasazawa Saho matatabi sir\u012bzu''|\u7b39\u6ca2\u5de6\u4fdd \u80a1\u65c5\u30b7\u30ea\u30fc\u30ba|extra=\"Sasazawa Saho's Matatabi Series\", 1972, Fuji TV}}.{{sfnp|Et\u014d|2005|p=148}} Toge/Mountain Pass series.{{Efn|Episodes: {{nihongo|''Nakayama-t\u014dge ni jigoku wo mita''|\u4e2d\u5c71\u5ce0\u306b\u5730\u7344\u3092\u898b\u305f|extra=\"At Nakayama Pass, Witness to Hell\"}}; {{nihongo|''Kuresaka-t\u014dge e no shiss\u014d''|\u66ae\u5742\u5ce0\u3078\u306e\u75be\u8d70|extra=\"To Kuresaka Pass Sprinting\"}}; {{nihongo|''Onikubi-t\u014dge ni suteta suzu''|\u9b3c\u9996\u5ce0\u306b\u68c4\u3066\u305f\u9234|extra=\"At Onikubi Pass, the Little Bells Cast Away\"}}}} Adapted from chapters in ''Mikaeri t\u014dge no rakujitsu'' (1970).{{sfnp|Et\u014d|2005|p=148}}\n*{{nihongo|''Jigoku no Tatsu torimonohikae''|[[:ja:\u5730\u7344\u306e\u8fb0\u6355\u7269\u63a7|\u5730\u7344\u306e\u8fb0\u6355\u7269\u63a7]]|extra=\"Tatsu from Hell's Casebook\", 1972-73}},  {{illm|Nihon Educational Television{{!}}NET|ja|\u65e5\u672c\u6559\u80b2\u30c6\u30ec\u30d3|preserve=1}}.{{sfnp|Et\u014d|2005|p=148}}\n*{{nihongo|''Hassh\u016b hankach\u014d''|[[:ja:\u516b\u5dde\u72af\u79d1\u5e33|\u516b\u5dde\u72af\u79d1\